ht fabrication on the part of less ethical individuals.)<\/p>\n\n<p>In summary: Massage has tangible benefits, but if the claims of the therapist sound too good to be true, they probably are.  <\/p>\n","answer_id":1596,"question_id":877,"up_vote_count":1}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/877/how-exactly-does-long-term-tension-over-months-build-up-in-the-ligaments-tend","last_activity_date":1335561159,"creation_date":1328137813,"answer_count":1,"title":"How exactly does long-term tension (over months) build up in the ligaments, tendons, muscles?","body":"<p>And is there any basis for believing that massage relieves that tension?<\/p>\n","question_id":877,"tags":["human-biology"],"score":7,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":137,"up_vote_count":7},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/5aab27ac128d8b89b554faa71f4b114d?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":777,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/777/ricardo-altamirano","reputation":140,"display_name":"Ricardo Altamirano"},"closed_date":1344584957,"answers":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/33a173fbc3159f90e6ecef38103850aa?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":584,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/584/thomasrive","reputation":563,"display_name":"thomasrive","accept_rate":29},"score":5,"is_accepted":false,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/5aab27ac128d8b89b554faa71f4b114d?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":777,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/777/ricardo-altamirano","reputation":140,"display_name":"Ricardo Altamirano"},"score":0,"post_id":1926,"edited":false,"creation_date":1335143229,"comment_id":2495,"body":"I don&#39;t suppose that book is available as a PDF too, correct?"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/33a173fbc3159f90e6ecef38103850aa?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"